OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid: Italy to require all
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworkers to show 'green     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpass' certificate          
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy is to make it compulsory for all 
OL,6, workers to have a Covid "green pass" - 
OL,7, proof of vaccination, a negative test  
OL,8, or recovery from the virus.            
OL,10,FThe measures are a first for Europe and
OL,11,Fsome of the strictest in the world.    
OL,13,FAnyone without a pass will reportedly  
OL,14,Fface suspension from work and may have 
OL,15,Ftheir pay stopped after five days.     
OL,17,FThe measure, due to come into force on 
OL,18,F15 October, aims to boost vaccinations 
OL,19,Fin a country that has been badly hit by
OL,20,Fthe virus.                             
